		<h2>寿命:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr">紀元1758-1819年頃</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
		<h2>称号・通称:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr">ハワイ諸島の王</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
		<h2>文明:</h2><div class="t"><div class="b"><div class="l"><div class="r"><div class="bl"><div class="br"><div class="tl"><div class="tr"><a href="CIVILIZATION_POLYNESIA.aspx" onmouseover="return tooltip('ポリネシア帝国');" onmouseout="return hideTip();"><img src="/civilopedia/images/small/CIVILIZATION_POLYNESIA.png" /></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
